WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.360
Adverse effects span the electrical and the

00:00:03.360 --> 00:00:03.840
mechanical.

00:00:03.840 --> 00:00:07.200
Watch for ventricular arrhythmias, from isolated PVCs

00:00:07.200 --> 00:00:08.640
to sustained VT.

00:00:08.640 --> 00:00:11.520
Conduction block may require temporary pacing.

00:00:11.520 --> 00:00:14.880
Fulminant cases can decompensate rapidly into cardiogenic

00:00:14.880 --> 00:00:16.800
shock requiring mechanical support.
